<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4A90E2;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-top: none;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #4A90E2;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .token {
            background-color: #e8e8e8;
            padding: 10px;
            font-family: monospace;
            word-break: break-all;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{tenantName}}</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Welcome, {{firstName}}!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for creating an account with {{tenantName}}. To complete your registration, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
        
        <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
        
        <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <div class="token">{{verificationUrl}}</div>
        
        <p>This verification link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
        
        <p>If you didn't create an account with {{tenantName}}, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{tenantName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated email, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
